 "title": "Steri Stumpie Pudding – from Mari-Louis Guy",
 "excerpt": "I saw the recipe on Mari-Louis Guy's page and it looked so lovely. Almost like an old-fashioned bazaar pudding made with Ideal milk. I asked her for the recipe and tried it out. Truly easy and delicious. I'll show you step by step how I made it. …",
 "seo": {
  "title": "Steri Stumpie-poeding - van Mari- Louis Guy - Marinda Kook",
  "description": null
 },
 "html": "<p>I saw the recipe on Mari-Louis Guy's page and it looked so lovely.  Almost like an old-fashioned bazaar pudding made with Ideal milk.  I asked her for the recipe and tried it out.  Truly easy and delicious.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://capetown.getitonline.co.za/wp-content/uploads/sites/15/2015/04/Steri-Stumpie-Jelly-Mould.jpg?d68cea\" alt loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>I'll show you step by step how I made it. Place your mould on a plate, otherwise it's hard to pick up.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-002.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2225\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-002-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 002\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>Get your mould and use a measuring cup to work out how much liquid the mould will take.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2226\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-003-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 003\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Heat a little of the Steri Stumpie and sprinkle your measured amount of gelatine over it so that it dissolves.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-010.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2229\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-010-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 010\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Remove from the heat and stir in the rest of the Steri Stumpie.  Pour into your container.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-007.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2227\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-007-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 007\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-013.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2230\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-013-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 013\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Place in the fridge overnight.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-014.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2231\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-014-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 014\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-020.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2232\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-020-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 020\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a>Unmould and enjoy.  It's truly delicious and easy.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-031.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-2236\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/steri-stumpie-poeding-031-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"steri stumpie poeding 031\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
 "recipe": null
}
